# MotherDuck has landed in Europe

MotherDuck is now available in the AWS eu-central-1 region. Get started with fast, serverless analytics with full EU data residency.

[LEARN MORE](https://motherduck.com/product/eu-region/#webinar-section)

MotherDuck is now available in Europe, contact us to get started.
